<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="313" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1426,1489]" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">
<taxonomicName box="[151,307,1426,1452]" class="Insecta" family="Margarodidae" genus="Margarodesia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,307,1426,1452]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Margarodesia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is an African genus. The only species, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Foldi" authorityYear="1981" box="[746,878,1426,1452]" class="Insecta" family="Margarodidae" genus="Margarodesia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="desmieri">
<emphasis box="[746,878,1426,1452]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">M. desmieri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[893,960,1426,1453]" captionStart="FIGURE 7" captionStartId="11.[151,250,1823,1847]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,182,1798]" captionTargetId="figure-15@11.[151,1436,181,1800]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIGURE 7. Margarodesia desmieri Foldi, adult female, from Foldi (2005a: 103, Fig. 10), reproduced with permission from Annales de la Société entomologique de France. A: antenna." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6332775" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6332775/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
), is a pest that feeds on the roots of 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Elaeis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="guineensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Elaeis guineensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[305,440,1462,1489]" name="Ivory Coast" pageId="12" pageNumber="313">Ivory Coast</collectingCountry>
; it may transmit plant pathogens (
<bibRefCitation author="Foldi, I." box="[819,947,1462,1488]" pageId="12" pageNumber="313" pagination="331 - 335" refId="ref28990" refString="Foldi, I. (1981) Margarodesia desmieri, n. gen. n. sp., cochenille Afro-tropicale nuisible au palmier a huile. Annales de la Societe entomologique de France, 17, 331 - 335." type="journal article" year="1981">Foldi 1981</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
